title: Sound On: WH Picks Fed Leadership
itunes:title: Sound On: WH Picks Fed Leadership
description:
Joe and Bloomberg Television anchor Caroline Hyde interviewed Virginia Senator Mark Warner and Director of the White House National Economic Council Brian Deese. Panel guests: Bloomberg politics contributors Jeanne Sheehan Zaino and Rick Davis. To listen on the Bloomberg terminal, click on the player thumbnail on the sidebar.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
